,"Manage your prospecting tasks in a way that promotes nonstop lead generation","And more!"]})]}),videos:l.xy,isNew:!1},{slug:"how-to-make-cold-calls-in-apollo",image:"/academy/images/learn-apollo-cards/cold-calls.png",type:s.gK.learn,useCases:[s.LD.outbound],features:[s.qT.search,s.qT.engagement],metaTitle:"Apollo Cold Calling: Free Course to Master B2B Sales Outreach | Apollo.io",metaDescription:"Learn proven Apollo cold calling techniques to find ideal prospects, build effective sequences, and close more deals. Free B2B sales training from industry experts.",title:"How to Make Cold Calls in Apollo",host:r.A.james,totalCourseLength:"25 minutes",coverImage:"/academy/images/course-cover-images/make-cold-calls-in-apollo.png",resources:[{text:"Resource Kit [PDF]",url:"https://21165194.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/21165194/LA%20Cold%20Calls%20Resource%20Kit.pdf"},{text:"Transcript [PDF]",url:"https://21165194.fs1.hubspotusercontent-na1.net/hubfs/21165194/LA%20Cold%20Calls%20in%20Apollo%20transcript.pdf"}],description:(0,a.jsxs)("div",{className:"space-y-6",children:[(0,a.jsx)(i.A,{variant:"h5",children:"Is cold calling dead? Not by a long shot. When done right and paired with a tool like Apollo, cold calling is a powerful way to boost your meetings booked."}),(0,a.jsx)(i.A,{children:"Join cold calling guru, James O’Sullivan, as he teaches how to use Apollo to turn your cold calls into hot leads."}),(0,a.jsx)(i.A,{children:"Whether you're new to sales or a seasoned professional, there’s something for everyone in this course."}),(0,a.jsx)(i.A,{children:"You’ll learn:"}),(0,a.jsx)(n.A,{color:"purple",items:["How the most successful sellers use cold calls as part of their outbound strategy","Which leads to prioritize for maximum impact","How to seamlessly integrate calls & voicemail scripts into your Apollo sequences","A simple cold calling framework anyone can follow","How to put it all together by watching James make *live* cold calls","And more!"]})]}),videos:l.